    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "Presented for your consideration is an exemplary specimen in pristine condition. This vehicle has been maintained to an uncompromising standard, exhibiting a flawless exterior finish and a cabin that retains its original factory luster. Every mechanical and aesthetic detail has been scrutinized to ensure it meets the requirements of the most discerning collector. This is a rare opportunity to acquire a vehicle of investment-grade quality that offers an unparalleled driving experience.",
